caption.p: Effects of 15-copaenol, epi-cubenol, and DCME extract on HeLa cell viability. The HeLa cells were incubated with different concentration of samples in a range of 125–0.5 μg/mL. Results are the mean ± SE, n = 3. The asterisk indicates significantly different from the control at the same level ( P < 0.05).
